### GET /api/v1/admin/tariffs/active
### Descripción: Obtener tarifa activa del tenant. Requiere Admin/Support + X-Tenant-Id.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>, X-Tenant-Id: <guid>
### Códigos: 200 OK (TariffPlanDto) | 404 NO_ACTIVE_TARIFF | 400

# @name getActiveTariff
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/tariffs/active
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}

### Response esperado (200): TariffPlanDto
### Response error (404): { "error", "code": "NO_ACTIVE_TARIFF" o "NO_APPLICABLE_TARIFF" }
